           Epsoc_phonon_along_Z
************************************************
************************************************
 Hamiltonian: H = H_k + \lambda * X1 * i sigma_y J^x + X2 * i sigma_x J^y

 ####################################
 #####  Monte Carlo parameter  #####
 ####################################
 nbin  =               5
 measurements in one_bin            800
 warmup  =            4000
 meas_interval  =               1
 meas_timerange  =               0
 total_iterations  =            8000
 number of mpi_blocks  =               8
 number of cores per block  =              24
 global update is not used

####################################
 #######  Physical parameter  #######
####################################
 lattice_dimension =            2
 Lt    =            1000
 dtau  =    0.100000000000000
 Beta  = dtau*Lt =  100.000000000000000
 lambda, el-phonon coupling =    0.800000000000000
Anti-aidabatic limit, M = 0.0
 disorder =    0.000000000000000
 filling  =    0.500000000000000
 N_up = N_down  =             196

List of observables, averages and errors
 Description: 
   e_PE = -U/2 * (n_up + n_down)^2 = -U/2*(n_up+n_down) - U*n_up*n_down
